Class Move

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.InstructionFormat
      • org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.Move

  • public final class Move
extends InstructionFormat
    The Move InstructionFormat class. The header comment for Instruction contains an explanation of the role of InstructionFormats in the opt compiler's IR.
